sentences: On 24 February 2013, Abudei released her 8-track EP Brown independently.
Brown was supported by the previously singles "Drift Away","The 90s Song" and "Out the Magazine".
It also contains cover versions of Aṣa's "Jailer" and Fela Kuti's "Trouble Sleep, Yanga Go Wake Am".

Abudei recorded "Abụ Ya", an acoustic solo that appeared on Brymo's seventh studio album Yellow (2020).
Prior to recording  "Abụ Ya", she released two singles in four years.
